class SalesPrediction { 
    double price; 
    int customerVisits;
    public SalesPrediction(double price, int promoHeld) { 
        this.price = price; 
        this.customerVisits = promoHeld == 1 ? (int)(price * 0.5) : (int)(price * 1.2); 
    }
    public double predictSales() { 
        return price * customerVisits; 
    }
}",

Upon seeing an increase in sales due to promotion, can we infer that the price was reduced?
